title: #522 - Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt
description:
Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt LIVE in studio and Joey tells Lee about the close relationship he had with his friend's grandmother and why she meant so much to him. Joey also tells us a story about his friend and boss in prison, Chicken Hawk.
